:1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>8點早一個字入，好似差唔多，一入去唔使招呼d 人太多 就開始食</blockquote><br />\n你諗多左, 咁耐都未試過8點有得食<br />\n8點鐘先叫人收麻雀入席, 好彩既都要8點半先上乳豬<br />\n最晏一單試過成9點幾, 有D住大西北既食完翅就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚我太遲去撞到新娘入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時係咪一齊入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddba5d84bc06ef235c26c40832aa228ba9b10b2e","tid":410642,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>8點早一個字入，好似差唔多，一入去唔使招呼d 人太多 就開始食</blockquote><br />\n你諗多左, 咁耐都未試過8點有得食<br />\n8點鐘先叫人收麻雀入席, 好彩既都要8點半先上乳豬<br />\n最晏一單試過成9點幾, 有D住大西北既食完翅就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚我太遲去撞到新娘入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時係咪一齊入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係出面等多陣咪得, 等佢入哂去再行都未遲<br />\n舊乳豬實等埋你"},{"pid":"5a159d4b403e7e489362e39b099c52b6a338b1b7","tid":410642,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"8點鐘吹起晚風"},{"pid":"9c14bdcfcf0649f9e00d1fd264a9b8a210c4781a","tid":410642,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"睇吓熟唔熟，唔熟又唔係真係咁想去就9點，去到多數有嘢食"},{"pid":"646a91d8597983dfe2fd77fed606d145fcd3e3d8","tid":410642,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊 今日要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd22c47ff863862e04defb3546f250ff73eadb3","tid":410642,"uid":39701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"